===== Application =====

This class is designed to work with applications. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:application:object#application|Application]]

Available methods: \\
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:application:create|application.create]]'' - creating new applications
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:application:delete|application.delete]]'' - deleting applications
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:application:get|application.get]]'' - retrieving application
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:application:massadd|application.massadd]]'' - updating application
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:application:update|application.update]]'' - adding items to applications
